      "id": "PopularPost363606",
      "post_content": "I just used this in the pre-release BNG draft. Maybe I was just unlucky but I kept getting 2 for 1'ed when I'd enchant it. The problem with this thing is everything kills it, being vulnerable to artifact and creature removal. I would recommend only bestowing it so you don't get 2 for 1'ed.",
